title: why is there still no new rotation
body: this is last weeks rotation.when will the new champ rotation take in place?

replies.body: That was a bug, sorry about that. [This](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/champions-skins/free-rotation/new-free-champion-rotation-jhin-kalista-kindred-more) rotation should be available this week.
